00:33:59,100 --> 00:34:00,660
 poput našega, koje nemaju

576
00:34:00,660 --> 00:34:02,720
 nikakvu industriju, nego samo

577
00:34:02,720 --> 00:34:05,020
 obavljaju usluge, se preljeva

